;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 503030201: Config/Level/Mission/5030302/Act/Act503030201.json-->
::'''Anderson:''' Greetings, {{MC|f=beautiful lady|m=handsome sir}}. It is an honor to meet such a {{MC|f=beautiful|m=handsome}} guest as yourself. Allow me to prepare a drink for you.
::'''Anderson:''' Well, this recipe is improved based on that famous Galaxy Ranger's recipe... rum, soda, lime, mint, and a touch of sugar, and you will get the unique mix: {{Rubi|Galactic Voyager|Mojito}}.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sounds good!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503030204-->
:::'''Anderson:''' Haha, I had a feeling you would enjoy it...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Isn't it too ordinary?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503030206-->
:::'''Anderson:''' Oh, my apologies... How about this? Blended with Kapo-Kali, Lemon Lazuli, golden pine nut, and orange crystal, with a subtle touch of absinthe and anise? I call it "Rebirth."
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} But I'm not an adult yet...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503030208-->
:::'''Anderson:''' Oh... my apologies... Let me prepare a more suitable drink for you.
:::'''Anderson:''' Here, a Penacony specialty &mdash; Classic SoulGlad, if you please.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_503030210-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503030210-->
::'''Anderson:''' I see you are not quite accustomed to this place... Are you new to Penacony?
::'''Anderson:''' If you are not in a rush to enter the dream world, please feel free to frequent here. This small bar has a huge stage...
::'''Anderson:''' With so many customers here, this place is a vast repository of information and a fertile ground for stories.
::'''Anderson:''' If you have questions or are seeking information, please come here and order a drink &mdash; a drink for a story. I guarantee my stories will satisfy your curiosity.
::'''Anderson:''' And of course, if you have splendid stories to exchange for drinks... I'd be delighted to hear them.
::'''Anderson:''' Here, this is on the house. Don't forget to come here often.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_404032601-->
;(Subsequent interactions)
