:{{DIcon}} Any recommended beverage?
::'''Anderson:''' Well, I believe each guest has their own "exclusive special drink."
::'''Anderson:''' However, as the bartender, I would like to recommend the most popular yet enjoyable option, the Classic SoulGlad.
::'''Anderson:''' I recommend trying this concoction, even if it's just to blend in.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_503030203_46-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503030203_46-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Do you enjoy gossiping?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503030235-->
:::'''Anderson:''' Well... don't you find the process of mixing drinks interesting?
:::'''Anderson:''' Combine base ingredients, both related and unrelated, in specific proportions to create a variety of intriguing beverages.
:::'''Anderson:''' To transform common ingredients into something extraordinary through certain rules and techniques... I find this process... fascinating.
:::'''Anderson:''' Therefore, what some may refer to as "gossip," or rather, the information and stories, can be treated as ingredients and mixed, gaining a richer flavor compared to mundane spices.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Why aren't you bartending in the Dreamscape?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503030240-->
:::'''Anderson:''' Hah... a great question. While I'm a bartender, I don't particularly enjoy the feeling of indulgence.
:::'''Anderson:''' People tend to indulge in fleeting, unreal pleasures, whether it's through wine or dreams.
:::'''Anderson:''' But to be honest, it doesn't appeal to me... People come to {{Rubi|the City of Dreams|Penacony}} to pursue what they cannot attain in reality. As for me, I am already content with my current life.
::;(If {{cx}}<!--Hidden Mission ID 4040326--> has been completed)
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::;(If {{cx}}<!--Hidden Mission ID 4040326--> has not been completed)
::::'''Anderson:''' Please take your drink, esteemed guest. I hope you find as much happiness in contentment as I do.
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_404032601-->
::::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I'm busy, so I'll be heading off.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503030245-->
:::'''Anderson:''' Take care. You are always welcome here.
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:{{DIcon|Exit}} See you next time.
::'''Anderson:''' Looking forward to seeing you next time.
